The '''Ancient Fruit''' is a [[Fruits|fruit]] [[Crops|crop]] that grows from [[Ancient Seeds]] after 28 days. Thereafter, the mature plant yields another Ancient Fruit every 7 days. Seeds can be obtained from a variety of sources (see [[Ancient Seeds]]).

