==Bundles==
* Five gold quality Ancient Fruit are an option for {{bundle|missing||y}}.
* Ancient Fruit is one of the options for {{Bundle|rare crops||y}}.

==Recipes==
Ancient Fruit is not used in any recipes.

==Tailoring==
Ancient Fruit can be used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create the dyeable [[Tailoring#Pants|Genie Pants]]. [[File:Genie Pants.png|36px]] It can be used in [[dyeing]], serving as a blue dye at the dye pots, located in [[Emily]]'s and [[Haley]]'s house, [[2 Willow Lane]].

==Quests==
Ancient Fruit is not used in any quests.

==History==
{{History|1.0|Introduced.}}
{{History|1.1|Reduced value to 550g, down from 750g.}}
{{History|1.4|Added as option for the Missing Bundle.  Can now be used in [[Tailoring]].}}
{{History|1.5|Iridium quality is now possible when using [[Deluxe Fertilizer]].  Bugfix for stages of growth (25% non-Agriculturist, 20% and 35% Agriculturist). Now used in the remixed Rare Crops bundle.}}

